title: KinetIQ framework from Humanoid orchestrates robot fleets
description:
Humanoid has introduced KinetIQ, an AI framework designed to orchestrate robot fleets across industrial and service applications.

The post KinetIQ framework from Humanoid orchestrates robot fleets appeared first on The Robot Report.
